This paper deals with the problem of transport-layer mechanisms over high-speed wireless links, specifically in the millimeter wave (mmWave) bands. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture). The paper also discusses congestion control and active queue management, which are topics related to information theory (cs.IT) and computer architecture (cs.AR). Additionally, the paper deals with mmWave links, which is a topic related to multimedia (cs.MM) and cryptography and security (cs.CR).
